text: Servance is a former commune. It is in Bourgogne-Franche-Comté in the Haute- Saône department in east France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune of Servance-Miellin.Arrêté préfectoral 26 September 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Haute-Saône
title: Servance
